  <entry>
    <title>使用 openGauss 作为数据源</title>
    <url>/2024/05/13/openGauss/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、前置准备"><a href="#一、前置准备" class="headerlink" title="一、前置准备"></a>一、前置准备</h2><ul>
<li>openEuler 操作系统</li>
<li>华为云 ECS</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二、使用华为云-ECS"><a href="#二、使用华为云-ECS" class="headerlink" title="二、使用华为云 ECS"></a>二、使用华为云 ECS</h2><h3 id="2-1-购买华为云-ECS"><a href="#2-1-购买华为云-ECS" class="headerlink" title="2.1 购买华为云 ECS"></a>2.1 购买华为云 ECS</h3><p>进入 <a href="https://www.huaweicloud.com/">华为云官网</a> 左上角找到如下产品</p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513212336022.png" class="" title="image-20240513212336022">

<p>进入后点击购买，在表单中选择如下：</p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513212823387.png" class="" title="image-20240513212823387">

<p>规格也可使用 2vCPUs/4GiB，为了更好的体验建议选择 4/8 组合</p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513213026573.png" class="" title="image-20240513213026573">

<p>上图为 <a href="https://docs.openeuler.org/zh/docs/22.03_LTS_SP2/docs/Installation/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87.html">openEuler 安装准备</a> 所建议的硬件配置</p>
<p>在规格右侧，有每种服务器的参考价格，可以选择自己想要的价格</p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513213842291.png" class="" title="image-20240513213842291">

<p>再往下便是选择系统镜像，我们选择 <code>openEuler 22.03 64bit(40GiB)</code>，系统盘则使用默认 40 则可</p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513214022881.png" class="" title="image-20240513214022881">

<p>点击右下角下一步，进入网络配置，若已有虚拟云，则可使用已存在的，或新建一个也可</p>
<p>在创建并选择网络之后，则需注意下方 <strong>公网带宽</strong> 项，将其选择为 <strong>按流量计费</strong></p>
<img src="/2024/05/13/openGauss/image-20240513214716207.png" class="" title="image-20240513214716207">

<p>带宽大小则按需选择，若是希望网络速度快一些则可选择 5Mbit，若是无文件下载上传需求则可选择 1Mbit</p>
<p>配置完网络则来到下一步高级配置，此处则是设置云服务器名称，系统登录密码，请各位自行设置</p>
<h3 id="2-2-登录系统"><a href="#2-2-登录系统" class="headerlink" title="2.2 登录系统"></a>2.2 登录系统</h3><p>点击华为云首页右上角的控制台，点击<strong>云服务器</strong> 进入控制台，在云服务器列表选择我们刚才购买的云服务器</p>
<p>此时界面显示服务器的具体信息，我们需要关注右上角，以后都可以在此对服务器进行开关机和登录操作</p>
<p>服务器开机状态下，点击远程登录，选择第一项，使用 <strong>CloudShell</strong> 进行登录</p>
<p>默认为 <strong>root</strong> 用户，使用密码认证，等待数秒后则可登录进操作系统</p>
<h3 id="2-3-配置系统"><a href="#2-3-配置系统" class="headerlink" title="2.3 配置系统"></a>2.3 配置系统</h3><h4 id="主机名"><a href="#主机名" class="headerlink" title="主机名"></a>主机名</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> 	<span class="comment">## 设置主机名</span></span><br><span class="line">[root@192 ~]<span class="comment"># hostnamectl set-hostname node0</span></span><br><span class="line">[root@192 ~]<span class="comment">#</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 重启</span></span><br><span class="line">[root@192 ~]<span class="comment"># reboot</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 重启后</span></span><br><span class="line">[root@node0 ~]<span class="comment"># hostname</span></span><br><span class="line">node0</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="防火墙"><a href="#防火墙" class="headerlink" title="防火墙"></a>防火墙</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看防火墙状态</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl status firewalld</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 状态为 inactive，则无需理会</span></span><br><span class="line">○ firewalld.service - firewalld - dynamic firewall daemon</span><br><span class="line">     Loaded: loaded (/usr/lib/systemd/system/firewalld.service; disabled; vendor preset: enabled)</span><br><span class="line">     Active: inactive (dead)</span><br><span class="line">       Docs: man:firewalld(1)</span><br><span class="line">       </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 否则需关闭</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 并禁用</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">disable</span> firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="关闭-SELINUX"><a href="#关闭-SELINUX" class="headerlink" title="关闭 SELINUX"></a>关闭 SELINUX</h4><blockquote>
<p>  修改 /etc/selinux/config 文件中的 “SELINUX” 值为 “disabled”</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用 vim 打开文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/selinux/config</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>按下 <code>/</code> 键进入搜索模式， 输入 <code>SELINUX</code> 在按下 <code>n</code> 则可定位至相应位置，按下 <code>a</code> 或 <code>i</code> 进入编辑模式，修改后按 <code>ESC</code> 退出编辑模式，再输入 <code>:wq</code> 保存并退出</p>
<h4 id="操作系统字符集"><a href="#操作系统字符集" class="headerlink" title="操作系统字符集"></a>操作系统字符集</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">env</span> |grep -i lang</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出</span></span><br><span class="line">LANG=en_US.UTF-8</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 否则执行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span>&gt;&gt; /etc/profile&lt;&lt;<span class="string">EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"># 输入，&gt;为一行：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&gt; export LANG=en_US.UTF-8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&gt; EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使参数生效</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="时区与时间"><a href="#时区与时间" class="headerlink" title="时区与时间"></a>时区与时间</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 ntp 服务</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install -y ntp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 开机启动ntp服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> ntpd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动ntp服务</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl start ntpd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查时区</span></span><br><span class="line">timedatectl |grep -i zone</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">Time zone: Asia/Shanghai (CST, +0800)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启用ntp服务</span></span><br><span class="line">timedatectl set-ntp <span class="built_in">yes</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编辑定时任务列表</span></span><br><span class="line">crontab -e</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">no crontab <span class="keyword">for</span> root - using an empty one</span><br><span class="line">crontab: installing new crontab</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看时间及时区</span></span><br><span class="line">timedatectl status</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">               Local time: Thu 2023-07-20 22:00:27 CST</span><br><span class="line">           Universal time: Thu 2023-07-20 14:00:27 UTC</span><br><span class="line">                 RTC time: Thu 2023-07-20 14:00:27</span><br><span class="line">                Time zone: Asia/Shanghai (CST, +0800)</span><br><span class="line">System clock synchronized: <span class="built_in">yes</span></span><br><span class="line">              NTP service: active</span><br><span class="line">          RTC <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">local</span> TZ: no</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="关闭交换内存"><a href="#关闭交换内存" class="headerlink" title="关闭交换内存"></a>关闭交换内存</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">swapoff -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="设置网络"><a href="#设置网络" class="headerlink" title="设置网络"></a>设置网络</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看网络接口名称</span></span><br><span class="line">ifconfig</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或者</span></span><br><span class="line">ip addr</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可看到如下输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">2: ens33: &lt;BROADCAST,MULTICAST,UP,LOWER_UP&gt; mtu 1500 qdisc fq_codel state UP group default qlen 1000</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">link</span>/ether 00:16:3e:xx:xx:xx brd ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff</span><br><span class="line">    inet 192.168.1.2/24 brd 192.168.1.255 scope global noprefixroute ens33</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置网卡MTU，MTU值推荐8192</span></span><br><span class="line">ifconfig ens33 mtu 8192</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看网卡MTU</span></span><br><span class="line">ifconfig -a |grep -i mtu</span><br><span class="line">ens33: flags=4163&lt;UP,BROADCAST,RUNNING,MULTICAST&gt;  mtu 8192</span><br><span class="line">lo: flags=73&lt;UP,LOOPBACK,RUNNING&gt;  mtu 65536</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> net.ipv4.tcp_retries1 = 5 &gt;&gt;/etc/sysctl.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> net.ipv4.tcp_syn_retries = 5 &gt;&gt;/etc/sysctl.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使参数生效</span></span><br><span class="line">sysctl -p</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ens33 需替换为自己的网络接口名称</span></span><br><span class="line">vim ifcfg-ens33 </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在文末追加 MTU=“8192”，重启生效。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="关闭-RemoveIPC"><a href="#关闭-RemoveIPC" class="headerlink" title="关闭 RemoveIPC"></a>关闭 RemoveIPC</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打开 logind.conf 文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim  /etc/systemd/logind.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改“RemoveIPC”值为“no” </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="修改-systemd-logind-service-文件"><a href="#修改-systemd-logind-service-文件" class="headerlink" title="修改 systemd-logind.service 文件"></a>修改 systemd-logind.service 文件</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打开systemd-logind.service文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim /usr/lib/systemd/system/systemd-logind.service</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改“RemoveIPC”值为“no”</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文件中没有配置参数，追加到文件的末尾即可</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新加载</span></span><br><span class="line">systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart systemd-logind</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="关闭HISTORY记录"><a href="#关闭HISTORY记录" class="headerlink" title="关闭HISTORY记录"></a>关闭 HISTORY 记录</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改根目录下 /etc/profile</span></span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置 HISTSIZE 值为0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 系统中 HISTSIZE 默认值为1000，将其修改为0。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使其生效</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编辑 sshd_config 文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注释掉 Banner 所在的行</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart sshd.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="系统相关"><a href="#系统相关" class="headerlink" title="系统相关"></a>系统相关</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"* soft nofile 1000000"</span> &gt;&gt;/etc/security/limits.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"* hard nofile 1000000"</span> &gt;&gt;/etc/security/limits.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h4 id="创建用户和用户组"><a href="#创建用户和用户组" class="headerlink" title="创建用户和用户组"></a>创建用户和用户组</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用户组：dbgrp</span></span><br><span class="line">groupadd dbgrp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用户：omm</span></span><br><span class="line">useradd -g dbgrp omm</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">'!Qwer432'</span> | passwd --stdin omm</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>  其中！Qwer432 为 omm 用户登录密码</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="下载相关包"><a href="#下载相关包" class="headerlink" title="下载相关包"></a>下载相关包</h4><p>访问 <a href="https://opengauss.org/zh/download/">openGauss</a>，选择 5.0.2，x86_64，openEuler 22，企业版，右键 <strong>立即下载</strong> 按钮，选择复制链接地址</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装依赖包</span></span><br><span class="line">dnf install -y gcc-c++ pcre pcre-devel zlib zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p /opt/software/openGauss</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> 755 -R /opt/software</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/software/openGauss</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载</span></span><br><span class="line">curl https://opengauss.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/5.0.2/x86_openEuler_2203/openGauss-5.0.2-openEuler-64bit-all.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压</span></span><br><span class="line">tar -zxvf openGauss-5.0.2-openEuler-64bit-all.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">tar -zxvf openGauss-5.0.2-openEuler-64bit-om.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="创建配置文件"><a href="#创建配置文件" class="headerlink" title="创建配置文件"></a>创建配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ./cluster_config.xml</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 粘贴如下内容</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;ROOT&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- openGauss整体信息 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;CLUSTER&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 数据库名称 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"clusterName"</span> value=<span class="string">"dbCluster"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 数据库节点名称(hostname) --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"nodeNames"</span> value=<span class="string">"node0"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 数据库安装目录--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"gaussdbAppPath"</span> value=<span class="string">"/opt/huawei/install/app"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 日志目录--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"gaussdbLogPath"</span> value=<span class="string">"/var/log/omm"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 临时文件目录--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"tmpMppdbPath"</span> value=<span class="string">"/opt/huawei/tmp"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 数据库工具目录--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"gaussdbToolPath"</span> value=<span class="string">"/opt/huawei/install/om"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 数据库core文件目录--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"corePath"</span> value=<span class="string">"/opt/huawei/corefile"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 节点IP，与数据库节点名称列表一一对应 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"backIp1s"</span> value=<span class="string">"192.168.192.129"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/CLUSTER&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;!-- 每台服务器上的节点部署信息 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;DEVICELIST&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 节点1上的部署信息 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;DEVICE sn=<span class="string">"node1_hostname"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!-- 节点1的主机名称 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"name"</span> value=<span class="string">"node0"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!-- 节点1所在的AZ及AZ优先级 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"azName"</span> value=<span class="string">"AZ1"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"azPriority"</span> value=<span class="string">"1"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!-- 节点1的IP，如果服务器只有一个网卡可用，将backIP1和sshIP1配置成同一个IP --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"backIp1"</span> value=<span class="string">"192.168.192.129"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"sshIp1"</span> value=<span class="string">"192.168.192.129"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!--dbnode--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"dataNum"</span> value=<span class="string">"1"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"dataPortBase"</span> value=<span class="string">"15400"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"dataNode1"</span> value=<span class="string">"/opt/huawei/install/data/dn"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;PARAM name=<span class="string">"dataNode1_syncNum"</span> value=<span class="string">"0"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/DEVICE&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/DEVICELIST&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ROOT&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>  注意：需将三处 192.168.192.129 改为自己服务器的私网 IP</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="2-4-安装"><a href="#2-4-安装" class="headerlink" title="2.4 安装"></a>2.4 安装</h3><h4 id="预安装"><a href="#预安装" class="headerlink" title="预安装"></a>预安装</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/software/openGauss/script</span><br><span class="line">./gs_preinstall -U omm -G dbgrp -X /opt/software/openGauss/cluster_config.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>遇到：</p>
<p>Are you sure you want to create the user [omm] (yes/no)? 输入 yes 并回车</p>
<h4 id="警告处理"><a href="#警告处理" class="headerlink" title="警告处理"></a>警告处理</h4><p>查看详情</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/opt/software/openGauss/script/gs_checkos -i A -h node0 --detail</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>A12</p>
<p>查看 ntp 状态，发现 ntp 没有启动</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status ntpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>启动 ntp 服务</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status ntpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="重新执行预安装"><a href="#重新执行预安装" class="headerlink" title="重新执行预安装"></a>重新执行预安装</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/software/openGauss/script</span><br><span class="line">./gs_preinstall -U omm -G dbgrp -X /opt/software/openGauss/cluster_config.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="错误处理"><a href="#错误处理" class="headerlink" title="错误处理"></a>错误处理</h4><p><code>/opt/huawei/install/om/script/gspylib/clib/libstdc++.so.6: version GLIBCXX_3.4.26' not found (required by libdnf.so.2)</code></p>
<p>方法：修改环境变量，让系统优先使用系统的目录下的 <code>libstdc++.so.6</code></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib64:<span class="variable">$LD_LIBRARY_PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h4 id="正式安装"><a href="#正式安装" class="headerlink" title="正式安装"></a>正式安装</h4><p>切换至 omm 用户</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su - omm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">gs_install -X /opt/software/openGauss/cluster_config.xml --gsinit-parameter=<span class="string">"--locale=en_US.utf8"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>期间被要求设置数据库密码</p>
<h4 id="安装验证"><a href="#安装验证" class="headerlink" title="安装验证"></a>安装验证</h4><p>查看安装的数据库状态</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gs_om -t status --detail</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出</span></span><br><span class="line">[   Cluster State   ]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cluster_state   : Normal</span><br><span class="line">redistributing  : No</span><br><span class="line">current_az      : AZ_ALL</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[  Datanode State   ]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    node node_ip         port      instance                            state</span><br><span class="line">--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">1  node0 192.168.192.129 15400      6001 /opt/huawei/install/data/dn   P Primary Normal</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><strong>服务器 IP 地址：</strong> 192.168.192.129</li>
<li><strong> 数据库的端口号：</strong> 15400</li>
<li><strong> 数据库数据路径：</strong> /opt/huawei/install/data/dn</li>
<li><strong>P：</strong> 安装时指定的角色为 Primary</li>
<li><strong>Primary：</strong> 实例为主实例</li>
<li><strong> Normal：</strong> openGauss 可用</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="三、使用-Navicat，Intellij-IDEA-等软件连接"><a href="#三、使用-Navicat，Intellij-IDEA-等软件连接" class="headerlink" title="三、使用 Navicat，Intellij IDEA 等软件连接"></a>三、使用 Navicat，Intellij IDEA 等软件连接</h2><p>openGauss 是基于 PostgreSQL 进行开发，所以数据库连接上可以使用 PostgreSQL 的 JDBC 驱动，也可在官方网站上下载 openGauss 的驱动，maven 上也有 openGauss 的 JDBC 依赖</p>
<p>但 opanGauss 需要配置一番才可允许远程连接，通常情况为了安全，我们不会让超级管理员能够通过远程连接</p>
<p>所以我们先创建一个用户，赋予其连接至某一数据库的权限，同时可赋予其表级的增删查改的权限</p>
<p>使用 root 或 omm 连接服务器，执行：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动 openGauss</span></span><br><span class="line">gs_om -t start</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 连接至任意数据库，这里使用 postgres</span></span><br><span class="line">gsql -d postgres -p 15400</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 连接权限</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="keyword">CONNECT</span> <span class="keyword">ON</span> DATABASE postgres <span class="keyword">TO</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 创建表的权限</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="keyword">ON</span> DATABASE postgres <span class="keyword">TO</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 指定数据库中 public 架构下所有表的查询权限</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">ON</span> <span class="keyword">ALL</span> TABLES <span class="keyword">IN</span> SCHEMA public <span class="keyword">TO</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 指定数据库中 public 架构下所有表的增删改权限</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> <span class="keyword">INSERT</span>, <span class="keyword">UPDATE</span>, <span class="keyword">DELETE</span> <span class="keyword">ON</span> <span class="keyword">ALL</span> TABLES <span class="keyword">IN</span> SCHEMA public <span class="keyword">TO</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 指定数据库中所有序列的使用权限（用于自增列等）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GRANT</span> USAGE <span class="keyword">ON</span> <span class="keyword">ALL</span> SEQUENCES <span class="keyword">IN</span> SCHEMA public <span class="keyword">TO</span> temp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>修改配置</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /opt/huawei/install/data/dn/pg_hba.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>往下翻可看到如下内容：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">TYPE  DATABASE        USER            ADDRESS                 METHOD</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"local"</span> is <span class="keyword">for</span> Unix domain socket connections only</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#表示只允许以安装时-U参数指定的用户从服务器本机进行连接。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">local</span>   all             all                                     trust</span><br><span class="line">IPv4 <span class="built_in">local</span> connections:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#表示允许omm用户从10.10.0.50主机上连接到任意数据库，使用sha256算法对密码进行加密。</span></span><br><span class="line">host    all           omm             10.10.0.50/32            sha256</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#表示允许任何用户从10.10.0.0/24网段的主机上连接到任意数据库，使用sha256算法对密码进行加密，并且经过SSL加密传输。</span></span><br><span class="line">hostssl    all             all             10.10.0.0/24            sha256</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#表示允许任何用户从10.10.0.0/24网段的主机上连接到任意数据库，使用Kerberos认证方式，当前版本暂不支持客户端kerberos认证。</span></span><br><span class="line">host    all             all             10.10.0.0/24            gss         include_realm=1 </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>在 IPv4 连接下增加自己希望的数据库，用户，IP 地址，方法</p>
<p>如：<code>host    postgres    temp    0.0.0.0/0    sha256</code>，表示允许 temp 用户从任意 IP 地址连接 postgres 数据库</p>
]]></content>
